translation[11]{c,v,t}:
  40,67,"Wahi to hai jisne tumko mitti se paida kiya, phir nutfey se, phir khoon ke lothdey se, phir woh tumhein bachhe ki shakal mein nilkalta hai, phir tumhein badhata hai taake tum apni poori taaqat ko pahunch jao, phir aur badhata hai taa-ke tum budhape ko pahuncho aur tum mein se koi pehle hi wapas bula liya jaata hai. Yeh sab kuch is liye kiya jaata hai taa-ke tum apne muqarrar waqt tak pahunch jao, Aur is liye ke tum haqeeqat ko samjho"
  40,68,"Wahi hai zindagi denay wala, aur wahi maut denay wala hai. Woh jis baat ka bhi faisla karta hai, bas ek hukum deta hai ke woh ho jaye aur woh jo jaati hai"
  40,69,"Tumne dekha un logon ko jo Allah ki aayaat mein jhagade karte hain, kahan se woh phiraye jaa rahe hain"
  40,70,Yeh log jo is kitaab ko aur un saari kitabon ko jhutlate hain jo humne apne Rasoolon ke saath bheji thi anqareeb unhein maaloom ho jayega
  40,71,"Jab tauq (fetters) unki gardano mein hongey, aur zanjeerein, jinse pakad kar"
  40,72,Woh khaulte huey pani ki taraf kheenchey jayenge aur phir dozakh ki aag mein jhonk diye jayenge
  40,73,Phir unse pucha jayega ke ab kahan hai Allah ke siwa woh dusre khuda jinko tum shareek karte thay
  40,74,"Woh jawab denge “khoye gaye woh humse, balke hum issey pehle kisi cheez ko na pukarte thay”. Is tarah Allah kaafiron ka gumraah hona mutahaqqiq (to stumble in error) kardega"
  40,75,Unse kaha jayega “yeh tumhara anjaam is liye hua hai ke tum zameen mein gair haqq par magan thay aur phir us par itratay thay
  40,76,"Ab jao, Jahannum ke darwazon mein daakhil ho jao hamesha tumko wahin rehna hai, bahut hi bura thikana hai mutakabbirin (proud) ka”"
  40,77,"Pas aey Nabi, sabr karo Allah ka wada barhaqq hai. Ab khwa hum tumhare saamne hi inko un buray nataij ka koi hissa dikha dein jinse hum inhein dara rahey hain, ya (ussey pehle) tumhein duniya se utha lein, palat kar aana to inhein hamari hi taraf hai"